"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"여기가 정말 하구미의 추억의 놀이동산인 거니?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event57-01-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","body":"응, 맞는 것 같아……\n하구미, 저 관람차랑 저 제트코스터도 기억하고 있는걸.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"event57-01-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"그, 그건, 하구미 짱이 어릴 적에\n있던 놀이기구가 아직도 있다는 거야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event57-01-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"보통 놀이기구는 점점 새로워지는데 말이죠.\n사람이 없는 이유를 대충 알 것 같기도……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event57-01-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"다들, 왜 그래?\n모처럼 놀이동산에 왔으니까 재밌게 놀자!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event57-01-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"아니~ 이런 애매한 놀이동산이면 이래 되지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event57-01-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"그치만 아직 여기서 놀지도 않았는걸. \n즐겁지 않다고 단정 짓기엔 아직 이르지 않을까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event57-01-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"듣고 보니 코코로가 말한 대로다.\n보이는 것만으로 판단해선 안 되는 것이지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event57-01-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","